{{Infobox Stadium | stadium_name = Gehaz El Reyada Stadium | image = | location = [[Cairo]], [[Egypt]] | opened = | renovated = | coordinates = | surface = Grass | tenants = [[Tala'ea El Gaish SC|Tala'ea El Gaish]] | seating_capacity = 20,000 (all seated) }}
'''Gehaz El Reyada El Askari Stadium''' ({{lang-arz|ستاد جهاز الرياضة العسكري}}), is a multi-use [[stadium]] with an all-seated capacity of 20,000 located in [[Cairo]] Governorate, [[Egypt]]. It is the home for [[Tala'ea El Gaish SC|Tala'ea El Gaish]].
