{{Infobox football club | clubname = Ittihad Fkih Ben Salah | image = <!-- [[Image:IRFBS-LOGO.jpg]] --> | caption = | fullname = Ittihad Riadh Fkih Ben Salah | nickname = | shortname = | founded = [[1962 in association football|1962]] | formernames = | dissolved = | ground = Stade Municipal de Fkih Ben Salah | capacity = | owntitle = | owner = | chrtitle = | chairman = | mgrtitle = | manager = | league = [[Botola 2]] | season = 2009–10 | position = 15th | website = | pattern_la1=_americamg14h| pattern_b1=_americamg14h| pattern_ra1=_americamg14h| pattern_sh1=| pattern_so1= | leftarm1= 009900| body1= 009900| rightarm1= 009900| shorts1= 000000| socks1= 000000| pattern_la2= | pattern_b2=_collar | pattern_ra2= | pattern_sh2= | pattern_so2= | leftarm2=0000ff| body2=0000ff| rightarm2=0000ff| shorts2=0000ff| socks2=0000ff| pattern_la3= | pattern_b3=_collar| pattern_ra3= | pattern_sh3= | pattern_so3=| leftarm3= ffffff| body3= ffffff| rightarm3= ffffff| shorts3= ffffff| socks3= ffffff| }}
'''Ittihad Fkih Ben Salah''' is a [[Morocco|Moroccan]] [[Association football|football]] club based in [[Fquih Ben Salah|Fkih Ben Salah]]. The club plays in [[Botola 2|GNF 2]] (Moroccan Second Division).
==History== The club spent 4 seasons in the 1st division between 1980 and 1984.
===Key dates=== * 1962 : Creation of the club * 1970 : Promoted to D2 * 1980 : Promoted to D1 * 1984 : Relegated to D2 * 2008 : Promoted to GNF2 (D2)
