'''Kahrabaa Ismailia Sporting Club''' ({{lang-ar|نادي كهرباء الإسماعيلية للألعاب الرياضية}}), is an [[Egypt]]ian football club based in [[Ismailia]], Egypt. The club is currently playing in the [[Egyptian Second Division]], the second-highest league in the [[Egyptian football league system]].

