'''Port Said Indoor Hall''' ({{lang-ar| صالة بورسعيد المغطاة}}) is an Olympic-standard, multi-use [[indoor arena|indoor sporting arena]] located in Al-Zohour district in [[Port Said]], [[Egypt]]. The capacity of the arena is 5,000 spectators. Hosts competitions of Handball, Basketball and Volleyball.
It was built in time for the [[1999 World Men's Handball Championship]].
