{{Infobox football club | clubname = SV Caiquetio | image = [[File:SV Caiquetio.svg|x200px]] | fullname = Sport Vereniging Caiquetio | nickname = | founded = | ground = | capacity = | chairman = | manager = | league = [[Aruban Division di Honor]] | season = [[2017–18 Aruban Division di Honor|2017–18]] | position = 9th }}
'''Sport Vereniging Caiquetio''', known as '''SV Caiquetio''', is an [[Aruba]]n [[football (soccer)|football]] club based in [[Paradera]], which currently plays in [[Aruban Division Uno]], the second tier of the national league, after being relegated from the [[Aruban Division di Honor]] in [[2013–14 Aruban Division di Honor|2013–14]].
