'''Stade de Malbaza''' is a soccer stadium in [[Malbaza]] Niger.  It can hold crowds of up to 2,000,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/venues/niger/stade-de-malbaza/|title=Stade de Malbaza|accessdate=7 September 2013}}</ref> both to watch [[FC Malbaza]] and regional tournaments such as the [[Tournoi de Grandes Vacances]] that showcases regional teams.

