'''Summers-Taylor Stadium''' is a [[college soccer|college]] [[soccer-specific stadium]] located on the campus of [[East Tennessee State University]] in [[Johnson City, Tennessee|Johnson City]], [[Tennessee]], in the [[United States]]. The stadium is home to the [[East Tennessee State Buccaneers]] [[East Tennessee State Buccaneers soccer|men's]] and [[East Tennessee State Lady Buccaneers soccer|women's]] soccer programs. The stadium opened in 2008 and sits 2,000 spectators.<ref name="stadium info">{{cite web|title=Facilities - ETSU Bucs|url=http://www.etsubucs.com/facilities/default/|website=[[East Tennessee State Buccaneers]]|publisher=East Tennessee State Athletics|accessdate=December 31, 2016}}</ref>

